# Authentication Setup Instructions:

# 1. BlueSky (FREE - Start here!)
# - Go to Settings > App Passwords in BlueSky
# - Create new app password
# - Use your handle and app password above

# 2. LinkedIn (FREE)
# - Go to https://www.linkedin.com/developers/apps
# - Create app with "Sign In with LinkedIn" permission
# - Generate access token for personal posting

# 3. Facebook (FREE)
# - Go to https://developers.facebook.com/apps/
# - Create app and get Page Access Token
# - Use Facebook Graph API Explorer to test

# 4. Twitter/X (EXPENSIVE - Avoided)
# - Basic API: $100/month
